OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA few
OL,6,Fshowers this evening, still wintry on
OL,7,Fhigh ground, then becoming dry
OL,8,Fovernight with clear spells. Winds
OL,9,Feasing and allowing a touch of frost.
OL,10,
OL,11,CMonday:FMostly dry on Monday, some
OL,12,Fsunshine but clouding over, patchy
OL,13,Frain for Isles where southerly winds
OL,14,Fwill strengthen later.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FSunny
OL,17,Fstart Tuesday, warm in east, then rain
OL,18,Freaching west later, some heavy.
OL,19,FOccasional rain or showers on
OL,20,FWednesday. Sunny intervals and showers
OL,21,Fon Thursday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
